### 🧪 RESTful API, HATEOAS, Content Negotiation, and Versioning HTTP Test Client

# Konfigurasi Environment
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

###
# =========================================================================
# 1. API VERSIONING TEST
# =========================================================================

# 1.1. Akses API V1 (Mendapatkan Produk dengan harga normal + HATEOAS)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products
Accept: application/json

###

# 1.2. Akses API V2 (Mendapatkan Produk dengan harga diskon 10% promo)
GET {{host}}/api/v2/products
Accept: application/json

###

# 1.3. Akses V1 menggunakan Query String Versioning (?api-version=1.0)
# (Menggunakan route segment fallback jika diizinkan)
GET {{host}}/api/products?api-version=1.0
Accept: application/json

###

# =========================================================================
# 2. CONTENT NEGOTIATION TEST
# =========================================================================

# 2.1. Request V1 dalam format JSON (Default)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products/1
Accept: application/json

###

# 2.2. Request V1 dalam format XML (Content Negotiation)
# Server akan secara otomatis merender XML karena AddXmlSerializerFormatters()
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products/1
Accept: application/xml

###

# 2.3. Request dengan format yang tidak disupport (Harus return 406 Not Acceptable)
# Karena ReturnHttpNotAcceptable = true dikonfigurasi di Program.cs
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products/1
Accept: text/plain

###

# =========================================================================
# 3. HATEOAS TEST & CRUD ACTIONS
# =========================================================================

# 3.1. Buat Produk Baru V1
POST {{host}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Sony WH-1000XM4",
  "description": "Noise cancelling wireless headphones",
  "price": 4200000,
  "stock": 15
}
